This software is written in the C++ programming language and uses the Qt
suite of libraries. You'll need both a C++ compiler installed as well
as Qt. You can obtain them from the following places:

	- http://gcc.gnu.org/
	- http://qt-project.org/

Simply execute the build script to build the application...

	$ ./build.sh

Installing the applcation is done with the following command (as root)...

	# make install
